      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-edt-cod-pdc-c01      .
           inspect   w-edt-cod-pdc-edm
                                      tallying w-edt-cod-pdc-c01
                     for   all "B"                                    .
           if        w-edt-cod-pdc-c01    >    zero
                     move  "B"            to   w-edt-cod-pdc-bwz
           else      move  spaces         to   w-edt-cod-pdc-bwz      .
